Package: dchunkr
Title: Work with Chunks of Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mauro", "Lepore", , "maurolepore@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1986-7988")),
    person("2 Degrees Investing Initiative", , , "contact@2degrees-investing.org", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Helps to work with chunks of data in parallel and to cache
    the results of each chunk. It's basic approach to handling somewhat
    large datasets and long runtimes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/2DegreesInvesting/dchunkr, https://2degreesinvesting.github.io/dchunkr/, https://github.com/maurolepore/dchunkr, https://maurolepore.github.io/dchunkr/
